Module eu.daproject.evl
Package eu.daproject.evl

Class InvokableMethod

java.lang.Object
eu.daproject.evl.InvokableMethod
Direct Known Subclasses:
MethodItem
public class InvokableMethod
extends Object
Class defining an invokable method for the EVL library as the extension of a MethodHandle with the caller object, the class tuple of "virtual" arguments and some additional data.
